flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B[Set character matrix]
    B --> C[Set password length to 8]
    C --> D[Set counter to 1]
    D --> E{Counter <= length?}
    E -- No --> I[Print password]
    I --> J[Exit]
    E -- Yes --> F[Generate random index]
    F --> G[Append selected character]
    G --> H[Increment counter]
    H --> E
